title: Ancient human activity dating back 4,000 years discovered in western Cyprus
description: NICOSIA, Jan. 23 (Xinhua) -- Evidence of continuous human activity dating back about 4,000 years has been discovered in the mountainous western Paphos district of Cyprus, the Department of Antiquities said on Friday. Read full story

title: At the heart of every Medjool date is an ancient palm
description: A legal battle over industrial pollution led researchers to a startling discovery in the Arava: a wild palm grove thousands of years old, belonging to a rare species never documented here and linked genetically to every domesticated date we eat
